#. <section class="sutta" id="sn12.15"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn12.15:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 12"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 12"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.15:0.2"
msgid "2. Āhāravagga"
msgstr "2. Fuel"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 15. Kaccānagottasutta → kaccāyanagotto (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn12.15:0.3"
msgid "15. Kaccānagottasutta"
msgstr "15. Kaccānagotta"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.17"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.15:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn12.15:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā kaccānagotto yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā "
"kaccānagotto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Kaccānagotta went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one "
"side, and said to him:"

msgctxt "sn12.15:1.3"
msgid "“‘sammādiṭṭhi sammādiṭṭhī’ti, bhante, vuccati."
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of this thing called ‘right view’."

msgctxt "sn12.15:1.4"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, bhante, sammādiṭṭhi hotī”ti?"
msgstr "How is right view defined?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.15:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Dvayanissito khvāyaṃ, kaccāna, loko yebhuyyena—atthitañceva natthitañca."
msgstr ""
"“Kaccāna, this world mostly relies on the dual notions of existence and non-"
"existence."

msgctxt "sn12.15:2.2"
msgid ""
"Lokasamudayaṃ kho, kaccāna, yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passato yā loke "
"natthitā sā na hoti."
msgstr ""
"But when you truly see the origin of the world with right understanding, you "
"won’t have the notion of non-existence regarding the world."

msgctxt "sn12.15:2.3"
msgid ""
"Lokanirodhaṃ kho, kaccāna, yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passato yā loke atthitā "
"sā na hoti."
msgstr ""
"And when you truly see the cessation of the world with right understanding, "
"you won’t have the notion of existence regarding the world."

#. VAR: Upayupādānābhinivesavinibandho → upāyupādānābhinivesavinibaddho (bj) | upāyupādānābhinivesavinibandho (s1-3, km, pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn12.15:2.4"
msgid "Upayupādānābhinivesavinibandho khvāyaṃ, kaccāna, loko yebhuyyena."
msgstr ""
"The world is for the most part shackled to attraction, grasping, and "
"insisting."

msgctxt "sn12.15:2.5"
msgid ""
"Tañcāyaṃ upayupādānaṃ cetaso adhiṭṭhānaṃ abhinivesānusayaṃ na upeti na "
"upādiyati nādhiṭṭhāti: ‘attā me’ti."
msgstr ""
"But if—when it comes to this attraction, grasping, mental dedication, "
"insistence, and underlying tendency—you don’t get attracted, grasp, and "
"commit to the notion ‘my self’,"

msgctxt "sn12.15:2.6"
msgid ""
"‘Dukkhameva uppajjamānaṃ uppajjati, dukkhaṃ nirujjhamānaṃ nirujjhatī’ti na "
"kaṅkhati na vicikicchati aparapaccayā ñāṇamevassa ettha hoti."
msgstr ""
"you’ll have no doubt or uncertainty that what arises is just suffering "
"arising, and what ceases is just suffering ceasing. Your knowledge about "
"this is independent of others."

msgctxt "sn12.15:2.7"
msgid "Ettāvatā kho, kaccāna, sammādiṭṭhi hoti."
msgstr "This is how right view is defined."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.15:3.1"
msgid "‘Sabbamatthī’ti kho, kaccāna, ayameko anto."
msgstr "‘All exists’: this is one extreme."

msgctxt "sn12.15:3.2"
msgid "‘Sabbaṃ natthī’ti ayaṃ dutiyo anto."
msgstr "‘All doesn’t exist’: this is the second extreme."

msgctxt "sn12.15:3.3"
msgid ""
"Ete te, kaccāna, ubho ante anupagamma majjhena tathāgato dhammaṃ deseti:"
msgstr ""
"Avoiding these two extremes, the Realized One teaches by the middle way:"

msgctxt "sn12.15:3.4"
msgid "‘avijjāpaccayā saṅkhārā;"
msgstr "‘Ignorance is a condition for choices."

msgctxt "sn12.15:3.5"
msgid "saṅkhārapaccayā viññāṇaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "Choices are a condition for consciousness. …"

msgctxt "sn12.15:3.6"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti."
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering originates."

msgctxt "sn12.15:3.7"
msgid "Avijjāya tveva asesavirāganirodhā saṅkhāranirodho;"
msgstr ""
"When ignorance fades away and ceases with nothing left over, choices cease."

msgctxt "sn12.15:3.8"
msgid "saṅkhāranirodhā viññāṇanirodho … pe …"
msgstr "When choices cease, consciousness ceases. …"

msgctxt "sn12.15:3.9"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hotī’”ti."
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering ceases.’”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn12.15:3.10"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
